item.title: Oppo Buds
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description:
• With Mic:Yes
  • Bluetooth version: 5.2
  • Battery life: 28 hrs | Charging time: 1.5 hrs
  • 10mm Dynamic Bass Boost Driver - Powerful & Rhythmic Bass
  • Enco Live Stereo Sound Effects | Dolby Atmos
  • AI Deep Noise Cancellation | 80ms Ultra Low Latency game mode
  • Intelligent Touch Controls | IPX4 Water Resistant
item.content:encoded:
• Double Tap: Play Music: Next Track. Call: Answer/Hang up the Call. Camera Control: Take a Photo. Triple Tap: Previous Track. Touch and Hold: The Left Earbud for 1s: Volume Down. The Right Earbud for 1s: Volume up. Both Earbuds for 4s when Wearing the Earbuds: Enter Pairing Mode. When Camera is Open, Double Tap either Earbud to take Photos
  • 10 mm Large Tetanized Driver (Stronger Bass); Enco Live Stereo Sound Effects (More Sound Effects); Up to 28 Hours of Listening Time (Longer Battery Life); AI Deep Noise Cancellation for Calls (Clear Calls); Binaural Low-latency with Bluetooth 5.2 Transmission (Faster and more Stable); Double-tap to Control Camera (More new Scenes).
